  "detailed_description": "Last Dino Standing is a hand-drawn 2D casual game where your goal is just to stay alive avoiding the crazy elements that fall from the sky. You're the <strong>last Tyrannosaurus</strong> alive in the dinosaur extinction event. We already know how this story ends, but you need to survive as long as you can.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Funny visuals.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple accurate movements.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 difficulty levels to choose from.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Timer system.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Map variations.</li></ul><br>and more secrets to discover.",
